GWindowEventHandler
public class GWindowEventAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements GWindowEventHandler

A basic adapter for GWindow event that defines empty methods for each of the interface's methods. Subclasses can override just the ones they are interested in. (For advanced use.)
